// Shared token fragments for __KEBAB__, reused across sizes with
// `map.merge()` (see all-buttons/button/tokens/_common.scss for the
// pattern).
//
// Carries one inert placeholder key so `$__KEBAB__-common-tokens` type-checks
// as a Sass map — a literal `()` type-checks as `list`, which trips
// `validate-config()`'s "tokens must be a map" check. Replace/remove the
// placeholder as you transcribe real M3 Expressive spec values (see
// docs/ai-handoff/COMPONENT-FACTORY.md §3); it is never emitted as CSS since
// the `mat.__OVERRIDES_FN__-overrides()` call in `_index.scss` starts out
// commented.
$__KEBAB__-common-tokens: (
  __KEBAB__-placeholder-token: null,
);
